<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">آخر:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَعْوَامُ لَهْوٍ كَانَ يُحْزِنُ ذِكْرُهَا ... قَلْبَ الَّلِبِيب لِفَقْدِهَا لِلَّطَاعَةِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لَوْ أَنَّهَا مُلِئَتْ بِذِكْرِ إِلَهَنَا ... وَتِلاوَةِ الْقُرْآنِ زَالَ نَدَامَتِي<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">آخر:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>قَدِّمْ لِنَفْسِكَ فِي الْحَيَاةٍ ... تَزوُّدَا فَلَقَدْ تُفَارِقَهَا وَأَنْتَ مُوَدَّعُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَاهْتَمَّ لِلَسَّفَرِ الْقَرِيبْ فَإِنَّهُ ... أَنَاي مِنَ السَّفَرِ الْبَعِيدِ وَأَشْنَعُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>واجْعَلْ تَزوُّدَكَ الْمَخافَةَ والتُّقى ... فَلَعَلَّ حَتْفَكَ فِي مَسَائِكَ أَسْرَعُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>